<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fa">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>اضافه کردن محصول</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #b92b27, #1565c0);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .card {
            background: #191919;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            width: 400px;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

            .card h1 {
                color: white;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .card .text-muted {
                color: #c1c1c1;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .card input[type="text"],
            .card input[type="password"] {
                border: none;
                background: none;
                display: block;
                margin: 10px auto;
                text-align: center;
                border: 2px solid #3498db;
                padding: 10px 15px;
                width: 85%;
                color: white;
                border-radius: 24px;
                transition: 0.25s;
            }

                .card input[type="text"]:focus,
                .card input[type="password"]:focus {
                    width: 90%;
                    border-color: #2ecc71;
                }

            .card input[type="submit"] {
                border: 0;
                background: #2ecc71;
                display: block;
                margin: 20px auto;
                padding: 10px 20px;
                width: 50%;
                color: white;
                border-radius: 24px;
                transition: 0.25s;
                cursor: pointer;
            }

                .card input[type="submit"]:hover {
                    background-color: #27ae60;
                }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
            <form id="Form" asp-controller="Product" asp-action="AddProduct" method="post" class="box">
                <h1>اضافه کردن محصول</h1>
                <p class="text-muted">لطفاً اطلاعات محصول خود را وارد کنید!</p>
                <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="نام محصول" required>
                <input type="text" name="price" placeholder="قیمت" required>
                <input type="password" name="categoryId" placeholder="شناسه دسته‌بندی" required>
                <input type="submit" value="افزودن">
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
